// BT-2842: subclass that inherits both `triggerBadArithDirect` and
// `triggerBadArithForwarded` from InheritedSelfSendErrorBase without
// overriding either. Neither selector is matched locally by Child's own
// dispatch/4 case statement, so resolving them requires
// `beamtalk_dispatch:super/5`'s hierarchy walk — the code path that
// previously masked the raw badarith as a bogus does_not_understand.

InheritedSelfSendErrorBase subclass: InheritedSelfSendErrorChild

  marker => #child
